Texts.Eng: Bring the ^orange;Cthulhu Statue^reset; to the ^green;obsessed scientist by the flower beds^reset; at the ^orange;Science Outpost^reset;

I am obsessed with ancient civilizations. Truly. I hear tell of an ^orange;elder race^reset; that once wandered the stars. If you can ^orange;bring me a Cthulhu Statue^reset; I would reward you very well.
This is a ^green;breathtaking specimen^reset;, but oddly maddening to look at. Your reward? Of course!
